		<h1>Medical Insurance</h1>
		<p>When you are living in Vietnam, it's important to have an International Medical Insurance. Accidents and emergencies are always unforeseen, and hospital system in Vietnam are not so good. Thus, having International Medical Insurance plan will give you peace of mind. We can design customised plan to fit your specific needs.</p>
		<p>Medical Insurance has a professional team with experiences on International Health Insurance. Our team members will corporate with you to find the best solution that fits your demand. We act on the client's behalf, and for the client's benefit, once you need us to take care of your insurance, we will give you the appropriate advice to settle your claim and maintain your insurance program.</p>
