		<h1>Our partners</h1>
		<h3>Liberty Mutual</h3>
		<div class="two-thirds"><p>"Helping people live safer, more secure lives", since 1912, Boston-based Liberty Mutual Insurance is a diversified global insurer and third largest property and casualty insurer in the U.S. based on A.M. Best Company's report of 2010 net written premium. The Company ranks 82th on the Fortune 100 list of largest corporations in the U.S. based on 2010 revenue. As of December 31, 2010, Liberty Mutual Group had $112.4 billion in consolidated assets, and $33.2 billion in annual consolidated revenue.</p></div>
