		<h3>Liberty Vietnam</h3>
		<div class="two-thirds">
			<p>Liberty has had a presence in Vietnam since 2003 when Liberty Mutual Group opened its first representative office in Hanoi. During the November 2006 APEC meeting, Liberty Vietnam were officially awarded the investment license to operate a 100% U.S.-owned general insurer in Vietnam.</p>
			<p>As a leading global insurer, Liberty is committed to protecting businesses and families in Vietnam with our locally customized insurance products.</p>
